{
  "stem": "1415.3",
  "chunk_idx": 9,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 62,
      "text": "Evidently, what happened is that maybe Mengele wasn't there.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 63,
      "text": "Evidently, what happened, they had no-- they had no designs what to do with us.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 64,
      "text": "Because we stood there naked for 24 hours on the platform-- just the women.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 65,
      "text": "And we were lucky.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 66,
      "text": "It was summertime.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 67,
      "text": "It was August.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 68,
      "text": "And [PAUSES FOR 3 SECONDS] all of a sudden, we were marched into a-- into a shower, [PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] and it wasn't the gas chamber.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 69,
      "text": "And by that time, already people knew what was happening there.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 70,
      "text": "The grown-ups knew.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 71,
      "text": "And I could hear things, and it was like rumors.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 72,
      "text": "And you don't want to hear it, but you hear it anyhow.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 73,
      "text": "But you watch.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 74,
      "text": "And you watch people's-- people's reactions and people's-- how they behave themselves.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 75,
      "text": "The behavior-- it was incredible.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 76,
      "text": "That-- that was my-- my good thing.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 77,
      "text": "I-- I watched.",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 78,
      "text": "Like I said, I took myself out of there as like I was watching from the outside.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 79,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 4 SECONDS] After the showers, [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] it could have been that after the showers, they-- they stood us there for 24 hours.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 80,
      "text": "It could have been before.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 81,
      "text": "I-- I-- I cannot exactly put it in the proper place, and I'm not going to try.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 82,
      "text": "All I know is we-- they marched us into-- into [GERMAN], they called it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 83,
      "text": "I was into numbers always.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 84,
      "text": "So we were in block 16 of the [GERMAN] or [GERMAN], they called it.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 85,
      "text": "And I remember I was in awe of seeing signs.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 86,
      "text": "There were signs posted everywhere, signs.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 87,
      "text": "And I didn't know where I learned how to read, but I wanted to learn how to read.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 88,
      "text": "And I must have learned it, because I-- I could read them.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 89,
      "text": "I could read the signs.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 9,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 90,
      "text": "And I was fascinated.",
      "word_count": 4
    }
  ],
